#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Mycus mod"
msgstr "真菌模组"

#. ~ Description for Mycus mod
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "For those who want to play as a mycus."
msgstr "适用于那些想扮演真菌的玩家。"

#: .\mutations.json
msgid "Mycus Identity"
msgstr "真菌身份"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mycus Identity'}
#: .\mutations.json
msgid ""
"We have synchronized our local physiology with that of our reproductive "
"systems.  Any spores we may encounter will not attempt to germinate inside "
"the local system."
msgstr "我们已将本地生理系统与繁殖系统同步。我们可能遇到的任何孢子都不会试图在本地系统中萌发。"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_male"
msgid "Fungus researcher"
msgstr "真菌研究员"

#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "profession_female"
msgid "Fungus researcher"
msgstr "真菌研究员"

#. ~ Profession (male Fungus researcher) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_male"
msgid ""
"Research seems to have to be interrupted by the fact that zombies have begun"
" to crawl outside. Is it fortunate that there is an infinite increase of "
"supplies? Let's use this body with fungal immunity."
msgstr "研究似乎因僵尸开始向外爬行而不得不中断。物资无限增加是幸运的吗？让我们利用这具具有真菌免疫力的身体吧。"

#. ~ Profession (female Fungus researcher) description
#: .\professions.json
msgctxt "prof_desc_female"
msgid ""
"Research seems to have to be interrupted by the fact that zombies have begun"
" to crawl outside. Is it fortunate that there is an infinite increase of "
"supplies? Let's use this body with fungal immunity."
msgstr "研究似乎因僵尸开始向外爬行而不得不中断。物资无限增加是幸运的吗？让我们利用这具具有真菌免疫力的身体吧。"

#: .\scenarios.json
msgid "Fungus Institute"
msgstr "真菌研究所"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Mycus' for a male character
#: .\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scenario_male"
msgid "Mycus"
msgstr "真菌"

#. ~ Name for scenario 'Mycus' for a female character
#: .\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scenario_female"
msgid "Mycus"
msgstr "真菌"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Mycus' for a male character.
#: .\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"When I finished writing a paper that advocated the usefulness of fungi, the "
"world was different. I understand that fungi are wonderful than anyone else."
" You can do enough in this new world."
msgstr "当我完成那篇倡导真菌实用性的论文时，世界已然不同。我比任何人都更了解真菌的奇妙之处。在这个新世界里，你足以大展拳脚。"

#. ~ Description for scenario 'Mycus' for a female character.
#: .\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_female"
msgid ""
"When I finished writing a paper that advocated the usefulness of fungi, the "
"world was different. I understand that fungi are wonderful than anyone else."
" You can do enough in this new world."
msgstr "当我完成那篇倡导真菌实用性的论文时，世界已然不同。我比任何人都更了解真菌的奇妙之处。在这个新世界里，你足以大展拳脚。"

#. ~ Starting location for scenario 'Mycus'.
#: .\scenarios.json
msgctxt "start_name"
msgid "Fungus Institute"
msgstr "真菌研究所"

#: .\item\ammo.json
msgid "spore mass"
msgid_plural "spore masss"
msgstr[0] "孢子团块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spore mass'}
#: .\item\ammo.json
msgid ""
"It is a spore extracted from a fungus. The stone is blown away using the "
"explosive power that spore bursts. It can be used as such, but it will still"
" be a lack of power for monsters."
msgstr "这是从真菌中提取的孢子。利用孢子爆裂的爆炸力可将石头炸飞。虽然可以这样使用，但对怪物来说威力仍显不足。"

#: .\item\ammo.json
msgid "large spore mass"
msgid_plural "large spore masss"
msgstr[0] "大型孢子团块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large spore mass'}
#: .\item\ammo.json
msgid ""
"It is a large spore isolated from a fungus. Although the productivity "
"dropped, I was able to greatly improve the power."
msgstr "这是从真菌中分离出的大型孢子。虽然产量下降了，但威力得到了极大提升。"

#: .\item\ammo.json
msgid "spores"
msgstr "孢子"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom cap"
msgid_plural "mushroom caps"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom cap'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a cute mushroom-shaped big hat with polka dots. The wide brim allows "
"you to protect your eyes from the sun."
msgstr "这是一顶可爱的圆点蘑菇形大帽子。宽大的帽檐可以保护眼睛免受阳光直射。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom helmet"
msgid_plural "mushroom helmets"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom helmet'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A brown mushroom helmet made of hardened fungi. The wide brim allows you to "
"protect your eyes from the sun."
msgstr "一顶由硬化真菌制成的棕色蘑菇头盔。宽大的帽檐可以保护眼睛免受阳光直射。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "armored mushroom helmet"
msgid_plural "armored mushroom helmets"
msgstr[0] "装甲蘑菇头盔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored mushroom helmet'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A brown mushroom helmet made of hardened fungi. Improved to be easier to use"
" as a protective gear."
msgstr "一顶由硬化真菌制成的棕色蘑菇头盔。经过改进，更适合作为防护装备使用。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom suit"
msgid_plural "mushroom suits"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇套装"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom suit'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a strange mushroom-shaped suit that wraps around the body. There is no"
" defense equal, but some warmth can be secured."
msgstr "这是一套包裹身体的奇特蘑菇形套装。虽然没有同等的防御力，但能提供一些保暖效果。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom armor"
msgid_plural "mushroom armors"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom armor'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It's hard to move, but the moss made of hardened fungus has defenses that "
"you can not think of as a mushroom."
msgstr "虽然行动不便，但这由硬化真菌制成的苔藓护甲，其防御力远超你对蘑菇的想象。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "improved mushroom armor"
msgid_plural "improved mushroom armors"
msgstr[0] "改良蘑菇护甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'improved mushroom armor'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a moss made of hardened fungus. The gentle surface works as an angle "
"for lunch. Much lighter than it looks and it makes it easier for you to "
"move."
msgstr "这是由硬化真菌制成的苔藓护甲。其柔和的表面在战斗中能起到偏转攻击的作用。它比看起来轻得多，让你行动更加自如。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom slippers"
msgid_plural "mushroom slipperss"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇拖鞋"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom slippers'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"These are lovely mushroom slippers. It is a bit unreasonable to run with "
"this."
msgstr "这是一双可爱的蘑菇拖鞋。穿着它跑步有点勉强。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom boots"
msgid_plural "mushroom bootss"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇靴"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'mushroom boots'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'armored mushroom boots'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'mushroom pouch'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'mushroom bag'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'mushroom backpack'}.
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "You sheath your %s"
msgstr "你将你的%s收鞘。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'mushroom boots'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'armored mushroom boots'}.
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "Sheath knife"
msgstr "收鞘刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom boots'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"Sturdy shoes made of hardened fungus. It wraps up both feet perfectly, but "
"it is a drawback that it is very thick and it is hard to walk."
msgstr "由硬化真菌制成的坚固鞋子。它能完美包裹双脚，但缺点是过于厚重，行走困难。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "armored mushroom boots"
msgid_plural "armored mushroom bootss"
msgstr[0] "装甲蘑菇靴"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored mushroom boots'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"Sturdy shoes made of hardened fungus. It's very light for defense, easy to "
"move and comfortable."
msgstr "由硬化真菌制成的坚固鞋子。就防御力而言非常轻便，易于移动且穿着舒适。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom gloves"
msgid_plural "mushroom glovess"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇手套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom gloves'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"These are gloves made of fungus. It does not get in the way of the "
"fingertips than I thought, and it is a good fit."
msgstr "这是用真菌制成的手套。它比想象中更不碍事，指尖活动自如，非常合手。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom gauntlets"
msgid_plural "mushroom gauntletss"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇护手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom gauntlets'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "Gauntlets made of hardened fungi. Its performance is quite good."
msgstr "由硬化真菌制成的护手。其性能相当出色。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "armored mushroom gauntlets"
msgid_plural "armored mushroom gauntletss"
msgstr[0] "装甲蘑菇护手"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored mushroom gauntlets'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"Gauntlet made of hardened fungi. Contrary to high defense, it is very light "
"and hardly disturbs movement."
msgstr "由硬化真菌制成的护手。虽然防御力高，但非常轻便，几乎不影响行动。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom cloak"
msgid_plural "mushroom cloaks"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇斗篷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom cloak'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A polka dot cloak made of fungus. Softly wrap the whole body, it is "
"comfortable to wear."
msgstr "一件由真菌制成的波点斗篷。轻柔地包裹全身，穿着舒适。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "armored mushroom cloak"
msgid_plural "armored mushroom cloaks"
msgstr[0] "装甲蘑菇斗篷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'armored mushroom cloak'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A cloak made of hardened fungus. This armor is highly resistant to "
"environmental pollution such as poison gas."
msgstr "一件由硬化真菌制成的斗篷。这种盔甲对毒气等环境污染具有高度抵抗力。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom gas mask"
msgid_plural "mushroom gas masks"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇防毒面具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom gas mask'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a gas mask made of hardened fungus. We integrated the know-how of the "
"protective armor and condensed the function to one mask. It is highly "
"resistant to environmental pollution such as poison gas."
msgstr "这是一个由硬化真菌制成的防毒面具。我们整合了防护装甲的专有技术，并将其功能浓缩到一个面具中。它对毒气等环境污染具有高度抵抗力。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom pouch"
msgid_plural "mushroom pouchs"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇小袋"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'mushroom pouch'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'mushroom bag'}.
#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'mushroom backpack'}.
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "Sheath sword"
msgstr "鞘剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom pouch'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"I hollowed out the contents of the mushroom and worked to use it as a pouch."
" The usability is really good. You can put the knife in a position where it "
"is easy to take out."
msgstr "我将蘑菇内部掏空，加工成一个小袋。实用性非常好。你可以将刀放在易于取出的位置。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom bag"
msgid_plural "mushroom bags"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom bag'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"I cut out the contents of a large mushroom and worked to use it as a "
"backpack. It is not too bad usability. You can put the sword in a convenient"
" position."
msgstr "我切出一个大蘑菇的内部，加工成一个背包。实用性不算太差。你可以将剑放在方便的位置。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom backpack"
msgid_plural "mushroom backpacks"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇背包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom backpack'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A backpack made of hardened fungi. We have made every effort to prevent "
"movement and make adjustments so that you can carry your luggage "
"comfortably. You can put the sword in an easy-to-use position."
msgstr "一个由硬化真菌制成的背包。我们尽力防止移动并进行了调整，让你能舒适地携带行李。你可以将剑放在易于使用的位置。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom legpouch"
msgid_plural "mushroom legpouchs"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇腿袋"

#. ~ Use action holster_msg for {'str': 'mushroom legpouch'}.
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "You stash your %s."
msgstr "你藏起了你的%s。"

#. ~ Use action holster_prompt for {'str': 'mushroom legpouch'}.
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "Stash ammo"
msgstr "藏匿弹药"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom legpouch'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a large magazine pouch attached to the legs. You can put only one "
"magazine in an easy-to-use position."
msgstr "这是一个附着在腿上的大型弹匣袋。你只能将一个弹匣放在易于使用的位置。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom shield"
msgid_plural "mushroom shields"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇盾牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom shield'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A small polka dot shield made of fungus. Because it was made on the fly, "
"there is only a quick performance."
msgstr "一个由真菌制成的小型波点盾牌。因为是临时制作的，所以只有快速性能。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "large mushroom shield"
msgid_plural "large mushroom shields"
msgstr[0] "大型蘑菇盾牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large mushroom shield'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A large shield made of hardened fungi. It is difficult to move, but has a "
"good defense."
msgstr "一个由硬化真菌制成的大型盾牌。移动困难，但防御力良好。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "improved large mushroom shield"
msgid_plural "improved large mushroom shields"
msgstr[0] "改良大型蘑菇盾牌"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'improved large mushroom shield'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"It is a large shield that can completely cover the whole body. It is "
"difficult to move, but has excellent defense."
msgstr "这是一个能完全覆盖全身的大型盾牌。移动困难，但防御力卓越。"

#: .\item\armor.json
msgid "mushroom umbrella"
msgid_plural "mushroom umbrellas"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇伞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom umbrella'}
#: .\item\armor.json
msgid ""
"A lovely polka-dot mushroom umbrella. You can prevent rain by equipping it "
"or holding it in your hand."
msgstr "一把可爱的波点蘑菇伞。装备它或手持它可以防雨。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus"
msgid_plural "mycuss"
msgstr[0] "菌类"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"At first glance it is a vegetable that is likely to cause harm to the body, "
"but depending on the recipe, it seems that you can eat various ways."
msgstr "乍一看是一种可能对身体有害的蔬菜，但根据食谱，似乎可以有多种食用方式。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "fluid sac"
msgid_plural "fluid sacs"
msgstr[0] "液囊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fluid sac'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"A fluid bladder from a plant based lifeform.  Not very nutritious, but fine "
"to eat anyway."
msgstr "一种来自植物基生命体的液囊。营养不丰富，但无论如何都可以食用。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "dry mycus"
msgid_plural "dry mycuss"
msgstr[0] "干菌类"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dry mycus', 'str_pl': 'dry mycuss'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It is fungi dried to protect it from corruption. It was carefully detoxified"
" and made. It can be stored for a long time by placing it in a suitable "
"environment."
msgstr "这是为防止腐败而干燥的真菌。经过仔细解毒处理制成。放置在适宜环境中可以长期保存。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus juice"
msgid_plural "mycus juice"
msgstr[0] "菌类汁"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus juice', 'str_pl': 'mycus juice'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It's bad for bad smell and bitterness, and unpleasant throat like sludge. "
"This drink has the effect of suppressing the attack of asthma."
msgstr "它气味不佳且苦涩，喉咙感觉像泥浆般不适。这种饮品具有抑制哮喘发作的效果。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus sandwich"
msgid_plural "mycus sandwiches"
msgstr[0] "菌菇三明治"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus sandwich', 'str_pl': 'mycus sandwiches'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid "Fungus-full veggies in bread."
msgstr "面包中夹满了菌菇蔬菜。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus salad"
msgid_plural "mycus salads"
msgstr[0] "菌菇沙拉"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus salad', 'str_pl': 'mycus salads'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"The platter is a name-only, pre-divided and cut-away item. It is not "
"delicious at all, as it has not been cooked well."
msgstr "这道菜只是名义上的，是预先分割并切好的物品。它一点也不美味，因为没有烹饪好。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "fried mycus"
msgid_plural "fried mycuss"
msgstr[0] "炸菌菇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fried mycus', 'str_pl': 'fried mycuss'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid "It's a very delicious, fried veggie."
msgstr "这是一种非常美味的炸蔬菜。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus pie"
msgid_plural "mycus pies"
msgstr[0] "菌菇派"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus pie', 'str_pl': 'mycus pies'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid "A delicious pie filled with delicious mycus mushrooms."
msgstr "美味的派，内馅是美味的菌菇蘑菇。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus pizza"
msgid_plural "mycus pizzas"
msgstr[0] "菌菇披萨"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus pizza', 'str_pl': 'mycus pizzas'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It is a mushroom pizza that can be eaten by vegetarians at ease. Delicious "
"milky lotion is used abundantly in thick fluffy fabric. It is the smell of "
"Maros that looks delicious."
msgstr "这是一种素食者可以安心食用的蘑菇披萨。美味的乳白色酱汁大量涂抹在厚实蓬松的面饼上。散发着诱人的马罗斯香气。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus soup"
msgid_plural "mycus soup"
msgstr[0] "菌菇汤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus soup', 'str_pl': 'mycus soup'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid "A nutritious, delicious and healthy mycus soup."
msgstr "一道营养、美味且健康的菌菇汤。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus tornado"
msgid_plural "mycus tornado"
msgstr[0] "菌菇龙卷风"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus tornado', 'str_pl': 'mycus tornado'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"The harmful part of the contaminated vegetables is alcohol pickled. Slightly"
" contains mutagens."
msgstr "受污染蔬菜的有害部分经过酒精腌制。略微含有诱变剂。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus alcohol"
msgid_plural "mycus alcohol"
msgstr[0] "菌菇酒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus alcohol', 'str_pl': 'mycus alcohol'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"A wonderfully savory mixture, fermented with an exquisite combination of "
"mycus mushroom and several kinds of ingredients. I promise that I can not "
"stop after drinking a bite."
msgstr "一种绝妙的咸香混合物，由菌菇蘑菇与多种配料精妙结合发酵而成。我保证喝上一口就停不下来。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus vodka (unfermented)"
msgid_plural "mycus vodka (unfermented)"
msgstr[0] "菌菇伏特加（未发酵）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus vodka (unfermented)', 'str_pl': 'mycus
#. vodka (unfermented)'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It is a primary moromi that has not finished fermentation. It is a sweet "
"liquid made by mixing enzyme-degraded persimmons and undigested persimmons "
"and vegetables."
msgstr "这是尚未完成发酵的初级醪液。一种由酶解柿子与未消化的柿子及蔬菜混合制成的甜味液体。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus vodka (undistilled)"
msgid_plural "mycus vodka (undistilled)"
msgstr[0] "菌菇伏特加（未蒸馏）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus vodka (undistilled)', 'str_pl': 'mycus
#. vodka (undistilled)'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It is a secondary mash that is not distilled after fermentation. It is not "
"delicious because it is mixed with alcohol and water with persimmons and "
"vegetables."
msgstr "这是发酵后未经蒸馏的次级醪液。由于混合了酒精、水以及柿子和蔬菜，味道并不好。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "mycus vodka"
msgid_plural "mycus vodka"
msgstr[0] "菌菇伏特加"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycus vodka', 'str_pl': 'mycus vodka'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It is a drink with a very delicious taste of persimmons. This newest brand "
"is a favorite item that can be called a symbol after the catastrophe."
msgstr "这是一种带有非常美味柿子口感的饮品。这个最新品牌是灾后堪称象征的受欢迎物品。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "protein block"
msgid_plural "protein block"
msgstr[0] "蛋白质块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'protein block', 'str_pl': 'protein block'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"We mixed flour with mycus mushroom and fluid sac and made it into a protein "
"with no moss. You can make something close to meat if you process it well."
msgstr "我们将面粉与菌菇蘑菇和液囊混合，制成了无苔藓的蛋白质。如果加工得当，可以做出接近肉类的食物。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "substitute coffee beans"
msgid_plural "substitute coffee beans"
msgstr[0] "替代咖啡豆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'substitute coffee beans', 'str_pl': 'substitute
#. coffee beans'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"Mycus rice cake and fluid sac were fried until it turned black and made it "
"coffee flavor. It is not good enough compared to the real thing, but it will"
" be a substitute for the time being."
msgstr "将菌菇米糕和液囊炸至变黑，制成咖啡风味。虽然与真品相比还不够好，但暂时可以作为替代品。"

#: .\item\food.json
msgid "Mycus milk"
msgid_plural "Mycus milk"
msgstr[0] "菌菇奶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mycus milk', 'str_pl': 'Mycus milk'}
#: .\item\food.json
msgid ""
"It is the one that collects and squeezes the latex that comes out when you "
"damage the brow. Those aged are transformed into milk by mycus."
msgstr "这是收集并挤压损伤菌菇时流出的乳胶制成的。那些经过陈化的乳胶被菌菇转化为奶。"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid "mushroom gun"
msgid_plural "mushroom guns"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇枪"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid ""
"I modified the spore sac and remodeled it so that it could be used as a "
"firearm. It's far from being a decent gun, but only the availability of "
"ammunition is unobtrusive."
msgstr "我改造了孢子囊，将其重塑成可用作火器的形态。它远算不上像样的枪，但只有弹药供应这一点还算不碍事。"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "pistol"
msgstr "手枪"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid "mushroom rifle"
msgid_plural "mushroom rifles"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇步枪"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid ""
"I modified the spore sac and remodeled it so that it could be used as a "
"firearm. The overall length was increased and some stability was obtained."
msgstr "我改造了孢子囊，将其重塑成可用作火器的形态。整体长度增加，获得了一些稳定性。"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "rifle"
msgstr "步枪"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid "mushroom smg"
msgid_plural "mushroom smgs"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇冲锋枪"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid ""
"It is a foolish-sized mushroom that can be said to be a collection of "
"mushroom guns. This load will handle most monsters. But it's really big."
msgstr "这是一种尺寸大到愚蠢的蘑菇，堪称蘑菇枪的集合体。这种火力足以应对大多数怪物，但体积确实非常庞大。"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自动"

#: .\item\gun.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "smg"
msgstr "冲锋枪"

#: .\item\item.json
msgid "minamata"
msgid_plural "minamatas"
msgstr[0] "水俣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'minamata'}
#: .\item\item.json
msgid ""
"It is the wisdom of the old-fashioned life that uses Minamata as a remedy. "
"The microbes in the blisters promote treatment."
msgstr "这是利用水俣作为疗法的古老生活智慧。水泡中的微生物能促进治疗。"

#: .\item\item.json
msgid "mycena chlorophos lamp (on)"
msgid_plural "mycena chlorophos lamp (on)s"
msgstr[0] "荧光小菇灯（开启）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'mycena chlorophos lamp (on)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'tukiyotake lamp (on)'}.
#: .\item\item.json
msgid "Close cover"
msgstr "关闭灯罩"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'mycena chlorophos lamp (on)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'tukiyotake lamp (on)'}.
#: .\item\item.json
msgid "I concealed the light emission part and made it not light."
msgstr "我隐藏了发光部分，使其不发光。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycena chlorophos lamp (on)'}
#: .\item\item.json
msgid ""
"Among the light-emitting mushrooms, the brightness of Yakutake is "
"particularly great. Furthermore, this Yakutake is mutated, and illuminates a"
" very wide area."
msgstr "在发光蘑菇中，夜茸的亮度尤为突出。此外，这种夜茸发生了变异，能照亮非常广阔的区域。"

#: .\item\item.json
msgid "mycena chlorophos lamp (off)"
msgid_plural "mycena chlorophos lamp (off)s"
msgstr[0] "荧光小菇灯（关闭）"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'mycena chlorophos lamp (off)'}.
#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'tukiyotake lamp (off)'}.
#: .\item\item.json
msgid "Open cover"
msgstr "打开灯罩"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'mycena chlorophos lamp (off)'}.
#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'tukiyotake lamp (off)'}.
#: .\item\item.json
msgid "I removed the cover and let the surrounding lights shine."
msgstr "我移除了灯罩，让周围的光线得以透出。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mycena chlorophos lamp (off)'}
#: .\item\item.json
msgid ""
"A cover is put on this Yakutake, and it is made not to shine. Remove to "
"brighten."
msgstr "这株夜茸被罩上了灯罩，使其不发光。移除灯罩即可变亮。"

#: .\item\item.json
msgid "tukiyotake lamp (on)"
msgid_plural "tukiyotake lamp (on)s"
msgstr[0] "月夜茸灯（开启）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tukiyotake lamp (on)'}
#: .\item\item.json
msgid ""
"Tukiyotake is widely distributed in Far East Russia and northeastern China, "
"centering on Japan. It is a kind of mushroom that belongs to the genus "
"Tsukiyotake of the genus Haratake eyes. It is light-emitting though weak."
msgstr "月夜茸广泛分布于俄罗斯远东地区和中国东北部，以日本为中心。它是一种属于原茸目月夜茸属的蘑菇，虽然发光微弱。"

#: .\item\item.json
msgid "tukiyotake lamp (off)"
msgid_plural "tukiyotake lamp (off)s"
msgstr[0] "月夜茸灯（关闭）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tukiyotake lamp (off)'}
#: .\item\item.json
msgid ""
"This Tsukiyotake is covered and covered so it does not glow. Remove to "
"brighten."
msgstr "这株月夜茸被罩上了灯罩，因此不发光。移除灯罩即可变亮。"

#: .\item\melee.json
msgid "mushroom staff"
msgid_plural "mushroom staffs"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇法杖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom staff'}
#: .\item\melee.json
msgid ""
"I converted a wood-like cocoon into a weapon. It is a stranger to look at "
"swinging the ax, but let's put up with it."
msgstr "我将一个木质的茧改造成了武器。挥舞斧头的样子看起来有些怪异，但请忍耐一下。"

#: .\item\melee.json
msgid "mushroom hammer"
msgid_plural "mushroom hammers"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇锤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom hammer'}
#: .\item\melee.json
msgid ""
"An umbrella with a hard stone like a hammer. It is inferior to a proper tool"
" and weapon, but it is quite easy to use."
msgstr "一把带有坚硬石质锤头的伞。虽然比不上正规的工具和武器，但相当好用。"

#: .\item\melee.json
msgid "mushroom sledge"
msgid_plural "mushroom sledges"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇大锤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom sledge'}
#: .\item\melee.json
msgid ""
"It is a hammer for crushing buildings, etc. Thanks to the adjustments made "
"to one point of power, it is very fragile and will break just by shaking it."
msgstr "这是一种用于粉碎建筑物等的锤子。由于力量集中调整于一点，它非常脆弱，轻轻晃动就会碎裂。"

#: .\item\melee.json
msgid "mushroom spear"
msgid_plural "mushroom spears"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom spear'}
#: .\item\melee.json
msgid ""
"It is a mushroom with a sharp umbrella. If you pierce into the enemy's body,"
" the umbrella will rotate and you will easily get a deadly wound through the"
" wound. The rotating umbrella also helps with corpse dismantling."
msgstr "这是一种伞盖尖锐的蘑菇。如果刺入敌人体内，伞盖会旋转，通过伤口轻易造成致命伤。旋转的伞盖也有助于尸体分解。"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom frame"
msgid_plural "mushroom frames"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom frame'}
#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "It is a big frame made of fungi. Used for vehicle construction."
msgstr "这是一个由真菌制成的大型框架。用于车辆建造。"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom roof"
msgstr "蘑菇屋顶"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom controls"
msgstr "蘑菇控制器"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "20L mushroom tank"
msgstr "20升蘑菇储罐"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "60L mushroom tank"
msgstr "60升蘑菇储罐"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom solar panel"
msgstr "蘑菇太阳能板"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom quarterpanel"
msgstr "蘑菇四分之一板"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "opaque mushroom quarterpanel"
msgstr "不透明蘑菇四分之一板"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom folding box"
msgstr "蘑菇折叠箱"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom door"
msgstr "蘑菇门"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "opaque mushroom door"
msgstr "不透明蘑菇门"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom wheel"
msgid_plural "mushroom wheels"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇轮"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom wheel'}
#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "It is a self-made wheel that is made by combining fungi."
msgstr "这是一个通过组合真菌制成的自制轮子。"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "steerable mushroom wheel"
msgstr "可转向蘑菇轮"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom plate"
msgid_plural "mushroom plates"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom plate'}
#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"It is a self-made armor made from fungi. Made of soft fiber, it is a vehicle"
" component that aims to absorb rather than prevent attacks."
msgstr "这是一种用真菌制成的自制装甲。由柔软纤维制成，是一种旨在吸收而非阻止攻击的载具组件。"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom plating"
msgstr "蘑菇装甲板"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom storage battery"
msgid_plural "mushroom storage batterys"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇蓄电池"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom storage battery'}
#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"A special processing is applied and it is mutated to a storage pot. The "
"capacity is small but you can not afford luxury."
msgstr "经过特殊处理，它变异成了一个储存罐。容量虽小，但你别无选择。"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom motor"
msgid_plural "mushroom motors"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇马达"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom motor'}
#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"It is a trap that moves rhythmically powered by electricity. This extremely "
"efficient device gives you amazing output."
msgstr "这是一种通过电力驱动、有节奏移动的陷阱。这个极其高效的设备能提供惊人的输出。"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom engine"
msgstr "蘑菇引擎"

#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid "mushroom seat"
msgid_plural "mushroom seats"
msgstr[0] "蘑菇座椅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mushroom seat'}
#: .\item\mycus_vehicle_parts.json
msgid ""
"Comfortable polka-dot seating made of fungi. Used for vehicle construction."
msgstr "由真菌制成的舒适波点座椅。用于载具建造。"

#. ~ Sign
#: .\map\mycus01.json
msgid ""
"This danger is dangerous! When the door opens, close the door! Fungal spread"
" can be prevented by a closed door!"
msgstr "这很危险！开门时，关上门！关上门可以防止真菌扩散！"

#. ~ Sign
#: .\map\mycus01.json
msgid ""
"Never shut the door! Never shut the door! Fungi is a friend if managed!"
msgstr "永远别关门！永远别关门！如果管理得当，真菌是朋友！"

#: .\map\mycus01.json
msgid "Mystery of Fungus Researchers"
msgstr "真菌研究者的谜团"

#: .\map\mycus01.json
msgid "Fungus grower"
msgstr "真菌培育者"
